# project.yml

- **Version:** `targets.HeartBit.info.properties.CFBundleShortVersionString` and `CFBundleVersion` must stay aligned with releases, [`Casks/heartbit.rb`](Casks/heartbit.rb), and GitHub tags `v*`.
